1. **Uključen** je alarm, niko ne sme da uđe u objekat. (The alarm is on, nobody is allowed to enter the building.)
2. Kada je baterija **uključena**, telefon se puni. (When the battery is connected, the phone is charging.)
3. Sve rasvete su **uključene** u ovom delu grada. (All the lights are turned on in this part of the city.)
4. Molim vas da se **uključite** u razgovor i date svoje mišljenje. (Please join the conversation and give your opinion.)
5. Zaboravila sam da sam ostavila peglu **uključenu**, srećom ništa nije izgorelo. (I forgot that I left the iron on, luckily nothing burned.)
6. Vlasnik stana nije **uključio** grejanje, pa je temperatura niska. (The apartment owner didn't turn on the heating, so the temperature is low.)
7. Da bi se koristio internet, morate da **uključite** Wi-Fi. (To use the internet, you need to turn on Wi-Fi.)
8. Pre nego što se uključite u ovaj projekat, morate biti upoznati sa svim detaljima. (Before you get involved in this project, you need to be familiar with all the details.)